<?Juror:🧑‍⚖️> **Jury** <?Juror:🧑‍⚖️>

The Jury is a trusted townsfolk group, with the special ability to investigate players. If fewer than two Jurors remain, the Jury is disbanded.
The Jury's first check happens during Night 2. If the Jury started with two Jurors they may check again each night. For every additional Juror the Jury started with they have to wait an additional night between checks.
The Jury is affected by weak disguises and obstructions.
